  "detailed_description": "Other Llamas spit at people and eat grass all day. But Pablo is different: <br>He explores ancient ruins built by the Inca Llamas of the past! 🏛<br><br>Running madly inside the temple, Pablo will find the truth about the native Llamas of a lost time - and get lots of shiny gold artifacts! 💎<br><br>Finish levels to get Llama-moneys - then use them to unlock new worlds or get loads of cool costumes! 🎉<br><br>🔑 Jump, Run, and Solve Puzzles!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483800/extras/072b8f424e5c1e02e3cb06186d5ee29e.poster.avif?t=1607602533\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483800/extras/072b8f424e5c1e02e3cb06186d5ee29e.webm?t=1607602533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483800/extras/072b8f424e5c1e02e3cb06186d5ee29e.mp4?t=1607602533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>🏁 Loads of cool levels, plus a shiny new endless mode and a challenging time trial!<br><br>🎮 Anyone Can Play!<br><br>🕶 Use your Llama-moneys to buy costumes and express yourself!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483800/extras/f49ff2d9007ee9538f42787646d3039d.poster.avif?t=1607602533\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483800/extras/f49ff2d9007ee9538f42787646d3039d.webm?t=1607602533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483800/extras/f49ff2d9007ee9538f42787646d3039d.mp4?t=1607602533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Other Llamas spit at people and eat grass all day. But Pablo is different: <br>He explores ancient ruins built by the Inca Llamas of the past! 🏛<br><br>Running madly inside the temple, Pablo will find the truth about the native Llamas of a lost time - and get lots of shiny gold artifacts! 💎<br><br>Finish levels to get Llama-moneys - then use them to unlock new worlds or get loads of cool costumes! 🎉<br><br>🔑 Jump, Run, and Solve Puzzles!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483800/extras/072b8f424e5c1e02e3cb06186d5ee29e.poster.avif?t=1607602533\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483800/extras/072b8f424e5c1e02e3cb06186d5ee29e.webm?t=1607602533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483800/extras/072b8f424e5c1e02e3cb06186d5ee29e.mp4?t=1607602533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>🏁 Loads of cool levels, plus a shiny new endless mode and a challenging time trial!<br><br>🎮 Anyone Can Play!<br><br>🕶 Use your Llama-moneys to buy costumes and express yourself!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483800/extras/f49ff2d9007ee9538f42787646d3039d.poster.avif?t=1607602533\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483800/extras/f49ff2d9007ee9538f42787646d3039d.webm?t=1607602533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483800/extras/f49ff2d9007ee9538f42787646d3039d.mp4?t=1607602533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
